            . I live at Epping-forest. On the 14th of December I called on a friend in <placeName id="t18290115-118-crimeloc610">Alpha-road</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18290115-118-crimeloc610" type="placeName" value="Alpha-road"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t18290115-118-crimeloc610" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18290115-118-off608 t18290115-118-crimeloc610"></join>; I left my two coats on my horse - I had not been in the house two minutes before the prisoner came and took them- I saw him through the window, and went out; he saw us, and threw down the coats - he went down a turning which is no throughfare; my friend got up to him and took him: we brought him back to the Nightingale public-house, and gave charge of him - I am quite certain of his person; I never lost sight of him - these are my coats.</p>
               <p>The prisoner put in a written Defence, denying that he had touched the coats.</p>
